             was indicted for <rs id="t18160110-91-off509" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18160110-91-off509" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160110-91-off509" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               feloniously assaulting 
                     
                        <persName id="t18160110-91-victim824" type="victimName">
                           Robert 
                           Langton
                        <interp inst="t18160110-91-victim824" type="surname" value="Langton"></interp>
